    "## Greeks Table Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "<center>\n",
    "\n",
    "| Greek    | Description        | Call                                                                     | Put                                                                      |\n",
    "|----------- |----------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ |\n",
    "| Delta ($\\Delta$) | Option's sensitivity to the underlying asset price | $\\Phi(d_1)$                                                             | $\\Phi(d_1) -1$                                                          |\n",
    "| Gamma ($\\Gamma$) | Delta's sensitivity to the underlying asset price| $\\frac{\\Phi'(d_1)}{S \\sigma \\sqrt{T-t}}$                              | $\\frac{\\Phi'(d_1)}{S \\sigma \\sqrt{T-t}}$                              |\n",
    "| Theta ($\\Theta$)|Option's sensitivity to the time  | $-rK\\Phi(d_2)e^{-r(T-t)} - \\frac{\\sigma S \\Phi'(d_1)}{2\\sqrt{T-t}}$ | $rK\\Phi(-d_2)e^{-r(T-t)} - \\frac{\\sigma S \\Phi'(d_1)}{2\\sqrt{T-t}}$ |\n",
    "| Vega ($\\nu$)  |Option's sensitivity to the underlying asset volatility  | $S \\Phi'(d_1)\\sqrt{T-t}$                                        | $S \\Phi'(d_1)\\sqrt{T-t}$                                        |\n",
    "| Rho ($\\rho$)  | Option's sensitivity to the risk-free interest rate | $K(T-t)e^{-r(T-t)}\\Phi(d_2)$                                            | $-K(T-t)e^{-r(T-t)}\\Phi(-d_2)$                                          |\n",
    "\n",
    "</center>"
